ðŸ§  Coding Standards for Cursor
React Architecture
Functional Components: Use const Component = () => {}.

Custom Hooks: Extract logic (e.g., useCharacters, usePagination) separate from UI.

Performance: Use useMemo for filtering lists.

Tailwind Usage
Utility-First: Avoid custom CSS classes unless for complex animations.

Gradients: Use subtle gradients for image overlays (bg-gradient-to-r).

Glassmorphism: Use backdrop-blur-md and bg-opacity for sticky headers/filters.

Animation Strategy
Page Load: Staggered fade-in for list items (items don't appear all at once).

Hover: scale-105 or translate-x for subtle feedback.